764
00:45:56.213 --> 00:45:57.267
No las comas entonces.

765
00:45:57.372 --> 00:45:58.638
Amígate. Pruébalo.
Dime lo que piensas.


766
00:45:58.693 --> 00:45:59.423
No.

767
00:45:59.465 --> 00:46:00.632
Vamos, pruébalo.

768
00:46:00.712 --> 00:46:01.610
No quiero.

